Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:33.90,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊 我看不见我是怎么死的了\N{\ren}Aah! I-I can't see my own death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.03,0:18:35.36,zh,,0,0,0,,我到底会怎么死啊\N{\ren}H-How am I gonna die?!
