Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:03.72,zh,,0,0,0,,我靠 啊啊啊\N{\ren}Shit! Aaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:07.06,zh,,0,0,0,,;;\N{\ren}Ugh! Aaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.81,0:19:14.27,zh,,0,0,0,,这是个什么教训\N{\ren}There's a lesson here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:17.11,zh,,0,0,0,,但我不想搞明白到底是什么了\N{\ren}and I'm not the one that's gonna figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:19.53,zh,,0,0,0,,呃 对不起 我没听你的话\N{\ren}Hey, uh, sorry I didn't listen to you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:21.28,zh,,0,0,0,,还打算毁灭世界什么的\N{\ren}and tried to kill the whole world and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:22.70,zh,,0,0,0,,我觉得我得学着\N{\ren}I guess I got to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:24.16,zh,,0,0,0,,更活在当下\N{\ren}how to live in the moment a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:26.20,zh,,0,0,0,,我的天 所以你今天还真学到了什么教训吗\N{\ren}Oh, boy, so you actually learned something today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:27.58,zh,,0,0,0,,你以为这是欢乐满屋吗\N{\ren}What is this, "Full House"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:29.08,zh,,0,0,0,,我今天倒是一直都活在当下\N{\ren}I was living in the moment all day,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.21,0:19:30.83,zh,,0,0,0,,导致我不停被纳粹杀死\N{\ren}and it kept getting me killed by Nazis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:33.08,zh,,0,0,0,,我觉得你不仅得活在当下 也得思考未来\N{\ren}I think you have to think ahead and live in the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.21,0:19:35.46,zh,,0,0,0,,Morty 我们在新闻上看见你了 你还好吗\N{\ren}Morty, we saw you on the news. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:38.51,zh,,0,0,0,,真有你的啊 Rick 你这是打算把我们儿子变成阿基拉吗\N{\ren}Oh, real nice, Rick. Turning our son into an Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.63,0:19:40.51,zh,,0,0,0,,-真有你的 -玩儿蛋去 Jerry\N{\ren}-Real nice. -Eat my ass, Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.63,0:19:42.18,zh,,0,0,0,,他是自己把自己变成阿基拉的\N{\ren}He turned himself into Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:44.93,zh,,0,0,0,,玩就玩 因为这是我的地盘 Rick\N{\ren}Oh, I'll eat it, because this is my house, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:46.60,zh,,0,0,0,,-我想玩儿什么蛋都行 -恶心\N{\ren}-I'll eat any ass I want. -Gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:48.35,zh,,0,0,0,,你说那个水晶不会伤害任何人的 爸\N{\ren}You said the crystals wouldn't hurt anyone, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:50.02,zh,,0,0,0,,这个家庭本有个崭新的开始\N{\ren}This family has a clean start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.14,0:19:52.27,zh,,0,0,0,,我不知道我儿子是不是适合去冒险\N{\ren}I don't know if adventures fit into my son's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:54.40,zh,,0,0,0,,我挺好的 别怪外公了\N{\ren}I'm fine. Get off Rick's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:56.86,zh,,0,0,0,,我做那些事情的时候 Rick甚至都不在这里\N{\ren}Rick wasn't even here when I was doing all that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:19:58.11,zh,,0,0,0,,都是我的错\N{\ren}That was all on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.23,0:20:00.03,zh,,0,0,0,,那好吧 Morty\N{\ren}Well, alright, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:03.28,zh,,0,0,0,,只要你没事就好 我们只关心这个\N{\ren}I guess, as long as you're okay, that's all we care about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:05.66,zh,,0,0,0,,我不想再看到任何夸张的事情\N{\ren}I don't want to see any more anime stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:07.33,zh,,0,0,0,,发生在我儿子身上了 老混蛋\N{\ren}happening to my son, buster.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:09.20,zh,,0,0,0,,那根手指染上艾滋病了 不是我的错\N{\ren}That finger has AIDs now. Not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.33,0:20:10.79,zh,,0,0,0,,你留下了艾滋病病毒\N{\ren}You skipped HIV?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.91,0:20:13.00,zh,,0,0,0,,-他跟你闹着玩儿的 宝贝 -但真的在刺痛\N{\ren}-He's messing with you, sweetie. -But it's tingling!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:15.46,zh,,0,0,0,,所以我想我们学到的教训就是各退一步\N{\ren}So, I guess what we learned is to split the diff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:16.63,zh,,0,0,0,,从现在开始 Rick和Morty会\N{\ren}From now on, Rick and Morty doing
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:18.00,zh,,0,0,0,,干点这个再干点那个\N{\ren}a little of this and a little of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:19.71,zh,,0,0,0,,是啊 有时我们会干些以前经常干的事情\N{\ren}Yeah, sometimes we'll do classic stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:20.97,zh,,0,0,0,,但别的时候 我们可以干其他任何事情\N{\ren}You know, other times, we'll do whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.09,0:20:22.30,zh,,0,0,0,,有时我们什么事也不干\N{\ren}Sometimes we won't even do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:23.76,zh,,0,0,0,,Rick和Morty 什么也不干\N{\ren}Rick and Morty do -- not doing anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:25.22,zh,,0,0,0,,一百年一万年 直到极限\N{\ren}-A hundred years! -Pushing it to the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.34,0:20:26.68,zh,,0,0,0,,Rick和Morty 不走寻常路\N{\ren}Rick and Morty, not sticking to one path.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:27.97,zh,,0,0,0,,尝试不同的事情\N{\ren}Trying different things,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:29.77,zh,,0,0,0,,绝不重复 永不乏味\N{\ren}Making sure to keep out of a rut.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:31.35,zh,,0,0,0,,干些事情 或者什么也不干\N{\ren}Doing stuff. Sometimes not doing stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:33.23,zh,,0,0,0,,甚至别去管有没有极限\N{\ren}Not even pushing a little bit towards the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:34.73,zh,,0,0,0,,分开干 一起干 一定要\N{\ren}Doing it alone or together. Making sure to keep our eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.85,0:20:36.40,zh,,0,0,0,,有收获 或者就只是放松一下\N{\ren}on the prize. Sometimes just relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.52,0:20:38.48,zh,,0,0,0,,或者不是 你他妈想干什么都行 Morty\N{\ren}Or not. And you can do whatever the fuck you want, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:40.48,zh,,0,0,0,,-就是这样 -等等 搞什么\N{\ren}-That's the end. -Wait, wait, what the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.61,0:20:42.36,zh,,0,0,0,,等等 你他妈刚说什么\N{\ren}H-Hold on. What the fuck did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:43.99,zh,,0,0,0,,没什么 我什么也没说啊\N{\ren}Nothing. I didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.11,0:20:45.61,zh,,0,0,0,,我只是在配合你们啊\N{\ren}I was just playing along with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:47.49,zh,,0,0,0,,你知道我什么都会录下来吧\N{\ren}You know I record everything, right?
