Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.83,0:20:53.96,zh,,0,0,0,,射在睾丸激素狂飙的\N{\ren}in a testosterone-addled
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:55.33,zh,,0,0,0,,三年级男孩的屁股里\N{\ren}fucking third-grade-boy cumfest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:20:56.67,zh,,0,0,0,,什么鬼啊 Summer 太恶心了\N{\ren}What, the hell, Summer?! That's disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:58.54,zh,,0,0,0,,恶心 Summer 我的天啊\N{\ren}Fucking gross, Summer! Jesus Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:21:00.63,zh,,0,0,0,,我只是在开玩笑啊 你们\N{\ren}I was just joking around, you --
