Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.14,0:21:09.51,zh,,0,0,0,,你把第四季首播给毁了\N{\ren}You ruined the Season 4 premiere!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:12.14,zh,,0,0,0,,第四季的首播 你毁了它\N{\ren}The Season 4 premiere, you ruined it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.51,0:21:45.26,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊 明天就是求职日了\N{\ren}God, tomorrow's career day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.38,0:21:47.76,zh,,0,0,0,,我根本不想去想毕业后我会做什么\N{\ren}I don't want to think about what I do when I get out of school.
