Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:51.64,zh,,0,0,0,,我想做临终关怀\N{\ren}I want to work in a hospice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:54.06,zh,,0,0,0,,我想去安慰那些将死之人\N{\ren}I want to comfort the people who are dying,
